Dialogs.Dialog: Nene
Hey... Can I ask you a question？
What is it？
Am I good for you？
Eh？ Why did you ask me all of a sudden...？
Because... I'm older than you... I wonder if you ever regretted it.
I've never regretted it. I love you. Our ages don't matter.
...I see. That's great.
That's my true feeling. Trust me.
Okay... I'm sorry. I was just a little worried.
Nene
...Hey, I want you to answer this honestly.
What is it？
What type of girl do you like？
Type...？
Well, for me, I'm the nosy type, right？
Is that so...？ I don't think you are...
And I'm older than you... Come on, most guys like younger girls, right？
That depends on each person's taste, though.
Are you forcing yourself to go out with me？
Absolutely no. Trust me, can you？
Okay. I'll trust you. Sorry for asking such a weird question.
Nene
Can I ask you a question？
Yeah. What is it？
What do you think about lovers？
When people are in love, they become lovers, right？
Hey, think more seriously.
Well... When you think that there's someone important to you and you want to be with that person. It's that feeling.
But, lovers these days break up very easily, right？ I wonder if we'll be okay...
Huh？
...Hehe, this question is probably still too difficult for you, right？
You're treating me like a child...
Nene
What triggers it when people fall in love？
What triggers it？
In the beginning, they were strangers, right？ But they meet and fall in love. They know it has to be this specific person...
Right... When I think about it, this is mysterious.
Yeah... We started out as strangers, but then we knew that it really had to be this one person...
It had to be？
Days and nights, you only think of this person... It's painful. It makes you feel happy and lonely at the same time.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, is that how you feel？
Hehe. Who knows？ I'm just a dreamy girl.
Nene
Hey, by the way, it's coming soon, right？
Eh？ What is it？
Eh？ Am I wrong？ It's your birthday...
I see. I totally forgot about it.
Geez, it's your own birthday... Ah, do you have something you want？
Hmm, there's nothing in particular that I want.
No~ You can tell me. It's a girlfriend's pleasure to celebrate her boyfriend's birthday, okay？
Okay...
Hehe. You can expect something nice.
(She looks happy. Anyway, I feel a little nervous to see her being in high spirits like that...)
Nene
By the way, about your birthday.
Hmm？ What is it？
How do you usually spend it？ Can you tell me？
I don't do anything special. People just say "Happy Birthday" to me and that's all.
That's all？ How about a celebration？
I used to do that... but not anymore.
It's fine if your friends don't celebrate it, but I'm your girlfriend, so it's different, okay？
It's different...？
It is different.
Okay, then. I don't really understand, though.
...Hehe, you're weird. Anyway, I think you're always like this.
Nene
I've been thinking about so many things...
What are you talking about？
About your birthday. It's coming up, right？
Ah, right.
What should I get as a present for you？ What do you want？
If you ask me all of a sudden like that... Well, I can't think of anything. Anything's fine, I think.
Geez, this is boring. You must have something that you want. Just tell me.
Then... What if I say I want ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？
...？ If ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ can be with me, that would be good enough.
You are... incredible.
(What...？)
Nene
By the way, about the birthday present...
Oh, my birthday...
I'll celebrate your birthday with you, so you just come to see me on that day.
Okay, thanks.
And then, about the present. What should I do？
You don't have to think about it that seriously. ...Anyway, I'm happy that you think about me.
Hmm, about that...
I want to make you happy. That's a sure thing. But, this is also what I do for myself.
What do you mean？
It's also fun for me to do something for my boyfriend. So, please let me enjoy it, okay？
Nene
Hah... Every year around this time, I always feel depressed.
Why？
It's almost my birthday again, you know？
Is that so？ We'll have to have a big celebration.
It's okay. I'm not... in the mood for a celebration.
...Why？
Because I'm getting closer to be an old woman...
Ah, is that so？
"Is that so？"...
But when I'm 90 years old, you'll be a 91 year-old grandma. We won't be much different, right？
You didn't have to try to say anything about it...
Nene
Although I hate it, my birthday is coming up.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, is there something you want？
Ah, are you going to give me a present？
What would you like？ I can splurge for it.
For that, I'll let you choose for me. It'd be boring if I know it in advance.
But I have no confidence. ...I have no clue what girls want.
If it's what someone we love chooses for us, anything will make us happy. That's how girls are...
Is that so？ Then...
Hey, just something simple is fine. Just something simple.
Nene
I'll be happy to celebrate my birthday with friends and family but it'd be best if I can celebrate it with the one I love.
Yeah, that's right.
But I've never thought I'd be able to have that chance.
No way. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. is pretty, so you must be popular among guys.
I'm not popular. I like to meddle with people's business and I think others think that I'm weird.
Really？ You like to take care of people and you're kind-hearted. Something like that makes people fall in love with you.
Did I say something weird？
...Yes, you did. You said it. ...Hehe.
What's the matter？
No, it's nothing. I just feel very happy.
Nene
My birthday is really coming up.
Yeah, pretty soon.
For me, if you just say "Happy Birthday" to me, that will be enough.
At that time, I want to show you what a nice boyfriend I am...
What you did for me is more than enough. You've already made me happy.
Did I do something for you？ I can't remember...
It's okay that you can't remember it. I'll never forget about it. That's good enough.
Nene
Hey, it's almost been a year...
What is it？
Geez... You didn't know？
Well... What is it again？
You and I. It's almost a year since we started dating, right？
Already a year？ It's so fast...
You really forgot about it... But I also think that time went by so fast...
Well... So, it's been a year since I started dating ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, huh？
Many things happened, right？
Do you feel like it's so amazing？ Actually, it's always been amazing that I can be with you...
...Yeah, I think so. Hehe. Yeah, you're right.
Nene
Hey, did you remember about last year？
...Yeah.
When I confessed to you, I was really nervous. I thought that you'd reject me because I was old than you.
Hey, age doesn't matter...
So we've started dating since then.
Yeah, that's right.
I'm quite surprised that we're now getting this close...
...We'll always be together like this from now on as well, right？
Yeah... But just aim for the next anniversary first. I'm getting older and older and you might start to dislike me.
That won't happen！ Even if you become an auntie or a grandma, I'll still love you.
Geez... I've never given it a thought that far. ...But I think you really mean it. I'm happy.
Nene
Hey, do you think I've changed during this one year？
Why do you ask me all of a sudden？
Come on. It's said that people will change when they're dating someone. So I wonder if I've changed.
Let me see. I feel like you've changed somehow, but...
Ah, so you can't tell. This is cruel.
How should I say it...？ It's not that you totally changed, but... Aaaah, sorry. I'm not good at explaining.
...You've never changed, huh？
Really？
Yeah... You're the same as always... Hehe.
I love ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ more and more, but I think I didn't change in other ways.
H-How can you say that with such a straight face...？ Aaah, you really haven't changed at all.
Nene
Do you remember what we've talked about earlier？
Well... When you asked me whether you've changed？
Yeah. I've been thinking about it. Actually, I think you've changed.
Really？ Hooray！
...What's with that reaction？
Come on, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. You said that people change when they're in love. But then you told me I hadn't changed at all.
A year before, I have no place in your heart, right？ But now, it's different.
Yeah. Right, it's totally different. And right now, I'm...
Don't say anymore！ I don't want to be overjoyed by the words from your mouth...
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you're so poetic...
Geez...
Nene
Can I ask you a question？
What？ Why do you become so formal？
Well, answer me honestly. Don't lie, okay？
Yeah... Okay.
Am I good for you？
Eh！？ There's nothing bad about you, okay？
Actually, you prefer a cute underclassman, right？
No way. I have only ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. And you already knew that...
Really？ If you lie to me, you'll be punished miserably.
I didn't lie！
(...Somehow, she's scary...)
Nene
I've been thinking about this sometimes...
What is it？
Would it be fun if we were in the same class？
Hmm... I wonder. I can't picture it, though.
Is it because I'm older than you that you couldn't picture being in the same class as me？
That's not the case. ...But I think it's good that ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is older than me...
Do you mean that any older woman would do for you？ So you just like older women in general, huh？
No. Of course, it can't be just anyone.
...Sorry.
I was just teasing you. I didn't mean to make you feel troubled like this. ...Forgive me, okay？
Nene
Hey, do you think you can tell when you start to love someone？
This is difficult... How about you, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？
Hmm, in my case... It starts when I want to know more about that person, I think.
It means you start to be interested in that person, right？
Yeah, it's that kind of feeling.
...And what will happen once you don't want to know about that person anymore？
Hehe. Could it be that you're getting worried？
Hmm... Well, maybe.
It's okay. Whenever I learn something about you, I even want to know you more.
Boys always think that girls are mysterious, right？ But it's the same to girls when they think about boys.
I see... Somehow I'm a bit relieved.
Nene
When someone you love loves you back, you feel happy, right？
Yeah, certainly.
But are you really satisfied with that？ Don't you want that person to love you more and more？
That's probably true.
It's like you want that person to know your feelings and return the feelings to you...
I understand that.
Hehe. I'm glad that I love you...
It makes me feel happy just because I love you.
If you feel the same way, I'd be even happier.
I feel the same...
(By the way, should I tell ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ about my birthday？)
Well, actually, it's going to be my bir--
Nene
Ah, right. Did you watch the late night movie last night？ It was an old romantic movie.
Eh？ No, I went to bed early last night...
Really...？ I didn't watch it either. I was thinking you could tell me what you think about it.
I see. By the way, it's almost my bir--
Ah！ Hey, hey. Speaking of which...
Yeah...？
(I can't cut into her conversation. I'll just talk about it later...)
(...Okay. Today, I'll tell ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ about my birthday.)
Nene
Ah, right. What do you think about a birthday party？
W-What do you mean？
It's understandable if you're in grade school... But my classmate actually held it.
Eh？ ...Is that so？
Don't you think it's embarrassing for a high school student to hold a birthday party？
But you want your close friends to celebrate your birthday with you, right？
I think that's embarrassing.
I-Is that so...？ Hah...
...What's the matter？ Hehe.
(Speaking of which, I still couldn't tell her about my birthday...)
Nene
Hehe... What's wrong？ Do you have anything you want to tell me？
Yeah... I do.
What could it be？
(But she said before that celebrating a birthday was embarrassing...)
Could it be something that you can't tell me？
That's not the case. It's just not that important.
Hmm？ So it's not important, huh？
Yeah, not important！ Hahaha...
I see. Then I don't have to care about it, right？ Hehe.
(It's almost my birthday. But... I still couldn't tell her about it...)
Nene
What's the matter？ You look very down.
Ah, no. It's not anything important, so...
But it's your birthday.
Yeah, my birthday... Eh！？
Geez... You overreacted.
Sorry... Ah！ Could it be that you knew it all along？
Hehe. Who do you think I am？ I'm your girlfriend.
Have you already planned about my birthday...？
Well, what do you think？ ...Hehe.
(She got me...)
(By the way, it's almost ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s birthday...)
Nene
Right. Are foreign soaps popular among your classmates？
Soaps？
Of course, I mean among the girls. I don't think there are any guys who fuss over soaps.
Hmm, I don't know about the girls. I haven't heard anyone mentioned about soaps, though...
The soaps are very popular in my class. People say they make your skin soft and smooth.
Hmm？ Is that so？
I'm already an old woman, so I have to worry about my skin.
Old woman...？ No way.
Hehe, I'm pretty concerned about it.
(She's that concerned about her age... I shouldn't mention her birthday now.)
(Right. I haven't talked about ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s birthday yet.)
Nene
Hmm？ What's the matter？
Well...
Hmm？
Umm...
Huh？ What's wrong？ Why do you look nervous？
It's...
Hehe. So, it's something you can't tell me？ Hmm... I see.
No, it's not...
Just kidding, kidding. Hehe, if it's not something perverted, I won't get mad at you, okay？
(...I'll wait until later.)
(It's going to be ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s birthday soon...)
Nene
Hmm？ What's the matter？ You seem to be nervous.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！ Well...
Ah... Don't tell me you don't love me anymore. Are you getting bored of me？
N-No way！！
Then did you fall in love with someone else？ Who？ Your classmate or someone in lower grade？
No, that's not it...
...If that happened, you must tell me, okay？ It's better than two-timing.
Nothing like that happened...
Hehe.
Nene
Hey... Lately, I think you've been trying to say something to me, right？
That's...
About my birthday, right？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, but you don't like to talk about your birthday...
Hehe... I think that you won't like it if I become an old woman.
I see... So from your point of view, you really see me as an old woman...
No, that's not it... I just...
Yeah, I know. Sorry. You're cute when you look troubled. I couldn't help teasing you.
Don't tell me you've been teasing me all along.
Hehe. I'll be looking forward to my birthday.
Nene
Ah, by the way, it's almost been a year now...
What is it？
Ah, you really don't remember.
Well...
Hehe. If you answer the next question correctly, I'll forgive you.
What question？
What was the date and month I confessed to you？
S-Sorry... I can't remember the exact date...
Did you know that girls always fuss over something like an anniversary？
...I'll reflect on this. Well... It was about a year ago... Ah！
You finally realized it, huh？ Yeah, we've been together for a year. Don't forget about it again, okay？
(I see. It's been a year already...)
A year has gone by... It's just a blink of an eye...
Nene
Yeah. It's really fast... Soon it'll be 5 years... and then 10 years...
How about after 50 years？ Does it called "golden wedding anniversary"？
That's for the case that we got married... If we stay together until then, I'll be an old grandma.
And I'll be an old grandpa.
...Hehe. You'll surely be a cute grandpa. Don't worry. I'll take care of you.
Why？ It's more likely that I'll be taking care of you, right？
I wonder. But it'd be hard for you. If you wouldn't take care of me properly, I'd surely get mad at you.
Nene
It's quite mysterious that we are walking together like this, right？
Really？ We are lovers, so I think this is just natural.
But a year ago, we were strangers. If we didn't meet at work, we wouldn't have known that we were in the same school.
I see... Yeah, you're right.
Hey, have you ever thought that you wanted to date a younger girl？
No way. For me, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is always the only one.
Supposed that I changed my job back then, would I be able to meet someone older？
Eh...？ Eh！？
If that happened, the one walking with me now wouldn't be you... Somehow this might be our fate.
W-Wait...！
Hehe. Just kidding. You're cute...
Nene
It's been another year that we've been together.
Yeah, that's right.
Although sometimes, you like to look at other girls...
No, no！ Don't make that up.
Hehe. I'm kidding. Just kidding.
Geez...
But I'm very happy. I'm glad I can be with you. Next year, and the year after that, we'll still be together, right？
Yeah, I promise.
Hey, how about we switch roles during next year？ You'll be an older brother who spoils me.
If I can choose, I want ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ to be an older sister and spoil me...
Really？ You know you're spoiled, huh？ Hehe. What should I do？
Nene
This might be abrupt, but I have a question.
What is it？
I've been thinking about this lately. ...Am I good for you？
...Why do you ask all of a sudden？
Because... Wouldn't it be more fun if your girlfriend is in the same grade or younger than you？
No, that's not true. Ages don't matter when it comes to someone I want to spend time with.
That's good then... But, I'm really worried.
You think too much.
But I was the one to confess to you...
Who confessed first doesn't matter. I love ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, okay？
Ah, wait. How did you say that here！？ Geez, this is embarrassing...
Nene
Hey... What did you think when I confessed to you？
What did I think？ Of course I was happy.
Really？ But I was always like that, right... Like, acting like your older sister...
Did you think I was acting like your stalker...？ That'd be detestable, right？
Hmm？ But because ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. That's why I love you...
...Did you intentionally say that to cheer me up？
No. It was my assurance.
...Then I can have confidence in myself, right？
Of course, you can.
Really？ ...Hehe. Now, I feel a little better.
Nene
The feeling of being in love is difficult to understand, right...？
What is this all about？
Like... It feels like something is piercing through your heart. Or whenever the phone rings, you feel very nervous...
Your heart？ The phone？
It feels like you're not yourself... Your heart keeps beating so fast and you think you become weird.
Sorry. I don't understand what you mean...
They are just for examples. But have you ever felt like that？
With something piercing, nervous feeling, and heart beating fast？ ...I feel like that when I go to the dentist.
Not that！ Geez. What's in your head！？
Nene
Do you remember what we talked about earlier？
When we talked about the dentist？
Seems like you remembered. But what I was trying to say was not about that.
Then...
Hey, can I ask you a question？ Do you love me？
Yes, I love you.
Okay... I see. I thought you'd say that.
It's obvious that I'd say that.
You just said that word naturally. Yeah, that's what you'd do when you love someone. Thank you...
Nene
Right. It's almost your birthday.
My birthday？ Yeah, it's pretty soon, right？
Geez... It's your own birthday. If you don't act more exciting about it, it'd be boring.
Okay. Thanks.
Hehe. You don't have to feel embarrassed. I can take any request from you, okay？
R-Request！？
I got some savings from part-time job. It's okay if you want to request something expensive.
N-No. I don't want anything expensive.
Hmm... Right. If it's something too expensive, you wouldn't feel good about it.
Yeah. Just your feeling is more than enough.
Nene
Right. What we talked about earlier...
Is it about my birthday？
Yeah. Is there something you want？
Something I want...？ Anything's fine for me.
Really？ This is boring. ...Then is there anything you want me to do for you？
Something I want you to do for me？ How about cleaning my room...？
Geez... I seriously want to celebrate your birthday for you.
Sorry... I'll try to think about it.
Nene
Ah, right. About your birthday.
Sorry. I've tried to think about what I want, but...
You want me to clean your room？
Eh？
Then I'll clean your room.
I can't tell whether you're joking or not...
To think about it, isn't it a girlfriend's privilege to clean her boyfriend's room？
That's true, but... Is it really okay？ I think I feel embarrassed about it...
Hmm... If you don't want me to, then I won't do it. ...Although I wanted to see your room...
Nene
To think about it, it'd be too much if I really go to clean your room, right...？
Is it about my birthday？
Yeah, I don't want to act like a stalker or something like that...
I wouldn't think of you like that. I just feel embarrassed...
Is it something that embarrassing？
Whatever. I'll only accept your feelings in this case.
Hehe. Then I'll have to prepare some present that contains more than just my feelings.
Will you give me a present？
Of course. You can start looking forward to it.
By the way, it's almost ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s birthday, right？
Nene
Eh？ What？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s birthday is pretty soon, right？
What is this about？
？ But it's ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s birthday...
Umm... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？
Hah... I'll be a year older...
(She doesn't have to concern about it that much...)
(By the way, I think ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ has been avoiding topics about her birthday...)
Nene
Hmm？ What's the matter？
I don't have any bad intention... but I'm really concerned. So, can I ask you...？
No！
Umm... Why do you hate to talk about your birthday so much？
I hate it. I really hate it.
Is it because... I'm younger than you？
It's not because of you. ...Come on. Women all care about their ages.
But I don't care...
Yeah, I know that... But this older sister is really worried about her age, all right？ Got it？
...Umm.
Nene
If you talk about my birthday again, I'll start crying.
...You won't get mad but you'll cry instead？
Yeah. I'll cry.
But... I don't know how to say this, but I really want to celebrate your birthday.
...Hmm. It's not like I don't understand you.
You understand？
...Well, how about I only accept your feelings for this？
My feelings？
Yeah, just your feelings would make this big sister happy enough. Hehe. Really.
Hey, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. How about a birthday present...？
Nene
You're talking about this again？ I told you that your feelings alone would be enough...
But I've been trying to think about it backwards.
...Backwards？
Yeah. If it was me and ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ did something for me on my birthday, I'd be very happy.
Hehe. You have been thinking about it that much.
So... What do you think？
That's still no good？
Okay, I got it. If you've tried this much, I can't reject it. But now I'm expecting something good. Are you well prepared？
Nene
A year passed by so fast...
Why are you saying that all of a sudden？
It's mysterious that it really continued on for a year.
What do you mean？
You really forgot it. Think about it. It's been a year for us！
...Ah！ So, that was one year before！？
Hehe. We started dating around this time last year. I was really nervous back then.
I was nervous too. To think that ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ confessed to me...
...Have you ever thought that it'd be better if we weren't together？
I've never thought about something like that. It's good that we're together like this, right？
Hehe. I give you a passing score for that answer.
Nene
It's really amazing...
What is？
That we're together like this.
We're lovers, so it's natural, right？
I didn't mean it that way... I mean the fact that I fell in love with you, confessed to you, and started dating you...
Yeah. We were just strangers to begin with.
Once I met you, gradually you had become the person I couldn't live without... Was it the same to you？
Yeah, it was the same to me.
Really？ Aren't you getting bored of me？ I'm older than you...
No, I won't get bored of you.
...I see. Yeah, it still feels fresh every time I meet you. I feel like I'm such a lucky person.
Nene
Hey, can we not celebrate our anniversary？
We don't really have to celebrate it, right？
Eh？ So, you don't care about it？
Well, soon it'll be our 5th anniversary, and then 10th anniversary and so on.
I should be happy to hear that. But if we think about the future, we should keep celebrating it from now on.
From now on？
Who knows when you might get in an accident, or being tempted by other girls？ I wish these would never happen.
Do I look like someone who'd easily get into accidents？
I don't know... Eh？ Now that I said it, I've become quite worried...
(How did our topic change from the anniversary to this...？)
Nene
I've been worried since then, but it seems like you didn't get in any accident, right？
Yeah... But I still have to always be careful.
Anyway, now I have another thing to worry about.
Another thing？
What if some young girl entices you and you also like her...？
Wait, wait！
In that case, I'll try to bear with it. If you just want to flirt with her...
Hey... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？
...Hehe. Do you think I'm serious？
Hey, don't tease me like that.
